587
00:40:29,400 --> 00:40:35,440
You will form a line! Move! Move!!
Just do what it says, everyone, OK?
Just... obey.

588
00:40:35,440 --> 00:40:39,680
The female is wise. 0bey!

589
00:40:39,680 --> 00:40:41,240
Report!

590
00:40:41,240 --> 00:40:46,280
