Superior intelligence.

611
00:41:53,000 --> 00:41:57,480
Intelligence scan - initiate.

612
00:41:58,840 --> 00:42:00,720
Superior intelligence.

613
00:42:00,720 --> 00:42:05,280
This one will become part
